description:
This utility enumerates all dialup/VPN entries on your computers, and displays their logon details: User Name, Password, and Domain.

You can use it to recover a lost password of your Internet connection or VPN.

Dialupass also allows you to save the dialup/VPN list into text/html/csv/xml file, or copy it to the clipboard.
summary: Recover lost dialup/RAS/VPN password in Windows XP/Vista
author: Nir Sofer
